@baseUrl = http://localhost:5140/api/inventory/search

# Requires Elasticsearch to be running

### Search all (match_all)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Full-text search for "jollof"
GET {{baseUrl}}?q=jollof

### Filter by itemType
GET {{baseUrl}}?itemType=restaurant

### Filter by ownerId
GET {{baseUrl}}?ownerId=rest-001

### Filter by availability
GET {{baseUrl}}?available=true

### Combined: search + filter + pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}?q=rice&itemType=restaurant&page=1&size=5

### Get item from Elasticsearch by ID (replace with actual ID)
@itemId = REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{itemId}}
